      <title>债券交易狂潮可能给做市商带来虚假的安全感</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/bond-trading-frenzy-risks-giving-market-makers-a-false-sense-of-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从表面上看，公司债券市场从未如此稳定和流动。在美国，9 月份的交易量创下了有史以来的最高纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/bond-trading-frenzy-risks-giving-market-makers-a-false-sense-of-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 18:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
